Package: metabigor
Version: 2.1.0
Architecture: all
Maintainer: Alienkrishn [Anon4You]
Depends: curl, tar, git, golang
Section: net
Priority: optional
Homepage: https://github.com/j3ssie/metabigor
Description: OSINT tool without API keys
 Metabigor is an intelligence framework designed to perform OSINT tasks
 without requiring API keys. Features include network discovery, ASN/IP
 lookups, and command-line search engine queries.
